title: Episode 05 Ft. Po Johnson

description:
The ladies welcome @thepojohnson from La La's Full Court life on this episode. In addition to flirting with Angela, GiGi and Stephanie, Po talks Caitlyn Jenner's transition and her own decision to "switch teams" back to men. Plus, the ladies open up about what the wildest thing they've ever done in the bedroom.
